{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-07",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友们大家好啊，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，今天是2026年7月7日。我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 7.314,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我是周航。苏晴今天挺精神啊。",
      "start": 8.763,
      "duration": 4.397,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那必须，今天的话题太对我胃口了。周航你知道吗，昨天有个新闻我看了好几遍都没缓过来。",
      "start": 13.657,
      "duration": 7.445,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哪个？",
      "start": 21.555,
      "duration": 0.522,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "就是有个中国公司跑联合国去了，给AI减负。你说这个事儿是不是听着就很带感？",
      "start": 22.482,
      "duration": 6.182,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "等一下，\"跑联合国去给AI减负\"，这个描述我得让你具体说说。",
      "start": 29.097,
      "duration": 5.79,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "情况是这样的，现在全球AI圈都在疯狂堆算力嘛，几万卡几万卡地烧，那叫一个卷。但这家公司反着来，它不堆算力，而是给机器人装了一套类脑架构，在联合国那个场合直接展示出来的。",
      "start": 35.352,
      "duration": 16.389,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这里面有个关键点——咱们一般人一听\"类脑\"都觉得是个噱头对吧？动不动就拿这个词出来吹。但这次不一样的是，人家是在联合国大舞台上拿出来的，而且强调的是\"降算力依赖\"这个落点。",
      "start": 52.203,
      "duration": 18.218,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，落点很重要。",
      "start": 70.872,
      "duration": 1.35,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说白了，类脑架构这条路之前不是没人走，但真正能跑到台面上讲故事的很少。这家公司敢在国际场合讲，而且讲的是\"让AI更轻\"，这个叙事其实挺聪明的。你想想，现在全球都在担心AI耗能的问题，对吧？",
      "start": 72.722,
      "duration": 18.697,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "真的假的，那能耗问题真的有那么严重吗？",
      "start": 91.857,
      "duration": 2.743,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你知道训练一次大模型碳排放多少吗？而且推理才是大头，每时每刻都在跑。这家公司的思路相当于告诉你：嘿，智能不一定非得靠堆GPU，结构上做文章也能行。",
      "start": 95.061,
      "duration": 14.977,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这个角度我特别喜欢。以前一提中国AI出海，大家印象里就是产品出海、APP出海，对吧？现在人家开始输出理念了，这不一样。",
      "start": 110.483,
      "duration": 10.58,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错，这是从\"卖货\"到\"立标准\"的转变。",
      "start": 121.537,
      "duration": 3.657,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哎，这话精准。那跟咱们有什么关系呢？周航你翻译翻译。",
      "start": 125.621,
      "duration": 4.702,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "翻译一下就是——以后你家里的扫地机器人、智能音箱，可能不需要那么贵的主芯片就能跑得很聪明了。成本下来了，价格才有可能下来。",
      "start": 130.787,
      "duration": 12.278,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，这个我喜欢听。",
      "start": 143.482,
      "duration": 1.829,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对了说到这个，我得提一嘴另一件事儿，可能很多听众没注意到。",
      "start": 145.747,
      "duration": 5.268,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "什么事儿？",
      "start": 151.432,
      "duration": 0.74,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "阿里和清华联合搞的一篇论文，拿了今年的ICML杰出论文。这篇论文干了什么呢？用一个极简方案，把扩散模型的推理效率给刷出了新纪录。",
      "start": 152.668,
      "duration": 11.668,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个你得展开讲讲。ICML，机器学习顶会的杰出论文，含金量很高的。",
      "start": 164.748,
      "duration": 7.184,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，而且重点是\"极简\"两个字。咱们现在生成一张AI图片，背后要跑好几十步的扩散过程对吧？很贵很慢。",
      "start": 172.411,
      "duration": 10.71,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是，这是扩散模型的老毛病了。",
      "start": 183.553,
      "duration": 3.091,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "阿里清华这个团队就证明了一件事儿——这个事儿不是必须的。结构上做简化，一样能逼近原来的效果，速度还快得多。",
      "start": 187.112,
      "duration": 9.056,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，这两件事儿其实是一条线上的。前面那个类脑架构是硬件层面的\"减负\"，这个扩散模型极简化是软件层面的\"减负\"。今天这个主题其实挺统一的。",
      "start": 196.658,
      "duration": 14.193,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，我看到那个采访里有个工程师说了一句话特别打动我，原话大意是：\"我们觉得，智能的下一个突破点不是更大的模型，而是更聪明的设计。\"",
      "start": 211.328,
      "duration": 11.668,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这话有点东西的。说白了，现在业界有个误区，好像参数越多越牛，算力越大越强。但实际上你看OpenAI也好、Google也好，最近的研究方向都开始往效率上靠了。这篇论文某种意义上就是给这股潮流添了一把柴。",
      "start": 223.414,
      "duration": 20.656,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，而且AIGC这个东西，推理成本才是真正的成本。你想想以后大家天天用AI生成视频、生成3D，那推理开销不得了？如果能把这个砍下来，对整个行业的商业化是连锁利好。",
      "start": 244.509,
      "duration": 16.041,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "所以端侧部署这个事儿，下次苏晴你可以专门做一期。",
      "start": 260.962,
      "duration": 4.223,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "行，记下来了。",
      "start": 265.678,
      "duration": 1.437,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "周航，咱们快讯部分今天也有几条挺有意思的，你想先聊哪个？",
      "start": 267.524,
      "duration": 5.094,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "OpenSquilla那个挺让人好奇的。0.5.0 Preview版本，直接登顶了一个叫DRACO的双榜。",
      "start": 273.105,
      "duration": 9.186,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦？DRACO我之前没怎么听说。",
      "start": 282.733,
      "duration": 3.135,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是个基准评测榜单，专门测多模型集成架构的。它最让人嘀咕的是对比名单里出现了一个叫Fable 5的东西，很多人猜这可能是某个下一代旗舰。",
      "start": 286.328,
      "duration": 15.412,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "真的假的？这名字我没听过。是你说它真是下一代旗舰？还是就是大家在猜？",
      "start": 302.211,
      "duration": 6.313,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个嘛，目前确实没有官方背书，就是社区在传。但你要说OpenSquilla这套多模型集成架构本身，确实是有看点的。你注意啊，它不是简单地调API拼一堆模型，而是有一套自己的调度逻辑。",
      "start": 308.936,
      "duration": 20.003,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我插一句——是不是类似那种\"哪个问题适合哪个模型就派谁去\"那种思路？",
      "start": 329.384,
      "duration": 6.661,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大致是这个意思，但比那复杂，还要考虑成本、延迟这些。",
      "start": 336.5,
      "duration": 5.007,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_038_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_038_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个思路其实挺对的，一个模型不可能啥都擅长，分诊制是迟早的事儿。",
      "start": 341.947,
      "duration": 6.269,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_039_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_039_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "还有一条快讯，联想控股牵头搞了个产学研创新生态工作委员会，跟中国中文信息学会合作的。我挺好奇这个事儿的，周航你给评评。",
      "start": 348.694,
      "duration": 11.624,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_040_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_040_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个事儿说白了就是大厂开始把\"高校关系\"做扎实了。中文信息处理这个领域其实挺特殊的，英文那边很多大模型拿过来直接用就行，但中文有自己的一套逻辑——成语、歇后语、古文这些，还有方言。",
      "start": 360.799,
      "duration": 16.738,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_041_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_041_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这个我深有体会。之前用某个英文为主的大模型，让它写个\"下雨天打孩子\"的下半句，它愣是给我编了一通。",
      "start": 377.963,
      "duration": 8.403,
      "audios": {
